				<font face="verdana" size="3" color="white"><a name="1">Scheduled Downtime: Postponed</a></font><br>
				<font face="verdana" size="2" color="white">
				<b><a href="mailto:eq_athelyn@hotmail.com" class="link">Athelyn</b></a>
				[8/26/2002-2:19:32 PM]</font>
				&nbsp;
				
				<a href="Comments.asp?ID=589613" class="link"><font face="Verdana" size="2">Comments[9]</font></a>
				
				<p>
				<font face="verdana" size="2" color="white"><blockquote>From EQ Live's <a href="http://eqlive.station.sony.com/support/scheduled_downtime.jsp"target=blank>Scheduled downtime page</a>:

<blockquote><font color=beige>Scheduled 8-28 Patch Postponed
Due to a need for more thorough testing, the EverQuest patch scheduled for August 28th at 3AM PDT has been postponed for a week and has been tentatively rescheduled for September 4th at 3AM PDT.<br><br>

-The EverQuest Operations Team</font></blockquote>

Please note that this message is an update from last week's patch announcement. The scheduled downtime has been pushed back from August 28th to September 4th.</blockquote></font></p><p>&nbsp;</p>
		
